Concrete Strength Prediction - Project_Prabhu_30Oct2020 Rev1 Resubmitted¶

Problem Statement: Concrete Strength Prediction¶

model tuning to obtain 85% to 95% accuracy.

Objective / Goal¶

To predict the concrete strength using the data available in file "concrete.csv". Apply feature engineering and model tuning to obtain 85% to 95% accuracy.

Data set¶

file : concrete.csv file

Attribute Information¶

Concrete data :Input and Output variables

  1. cement : Cement (cement) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  2. slag : Blast Furnace Slag (slag) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  3. ash : Fly Ash (ash) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  4. water : Water(water) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  5. superplastic : Superplasticizer (superplastic) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  6. coarseagg : Coarse Aggregate (coarseagg) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  7. fineagg : Fine Aggregate (fineagg) quantitative kg in a m3 mixture -- Input Variable
  8. age : Age(age) quantitative Day (1~365) -- Input Variable
  9. strength : Concrete compressive strength(strength) quantitative MPa -- Output Variable
